      <title>奥尔班称匈牙利致力于保持通过乌克兰的天然气运输畅通</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/hungary-working-to-keep-gas-transit-via-ukraine-open-orban-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班表示，匈牙利正在寻求一种解决方案，以便在莫斯科和基辅之间的现有过境合同到期后，继续通过乌克兰向欧洲输送天然气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/hungary-working-to-keep-gas-transit-via-ukraine-open-orban-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 12:30:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国巴黎银行签署 51 亿欧元协议收购安盛资产管理公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/bnp-paribas-signs-5-1-billion-deal-to-buy-axa-s-asset-manager</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国巴黎银行最终以 51 亿欧元（53 亿美元）收购法国安盛银行的资产管理部门，这是首席执行官让·罗兰·博纳菲 (Jean-Laurent Bonnafe) 任职期间进行的最大一笔收购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/bnp-paribas-signs-5-1-billion-deal-to-buy-axa-s-asset-manager</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 11:49:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
