      <title>俄罗斯向中国输送天然气日均量创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/russia-s-daily-pipeline-gas-flows-to-china-set-new-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据能源巨头俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司称，12 月 20 日，俄罗斯通过西伯利亚力量管道向中国输送的天然气日流量创下了新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/russia-s-daily-pipeline-gas-flows-to-china-set-new-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 11:25:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
