      <title>绿色氢气从被大肆宣传到因成本惊人而备受冷落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/green-hydrogen-goes-from-hyped-to-humbled-on-eye-popping-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于成本下降的预期未能实现，今年大量生产绿色氢（一种被认为对于实现净零排放至关重要的燃料）的项目被放弃。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/green-hydrogen-goes-from-hyped-to-humbled-on-eye-popping-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>可可将成为 2024 年最大的商品赢家。一切尚未结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/cocoa-caps-2024-as-biggest-commodity-winner-it-s-not-over-yet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2024 年，可可的涨势已超越所有主要大宗商品，而且几乎没有迹象表明导致其近乎垂直的轨迹的供应紧张和脆弱的交易格局会得到快速解决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/cocoa-caps-2024-as-biggest-commodity-winner-it-s-not-over-yet</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
