      <title>Party City 第二次申请破产 零售业重现昔日辉煌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/party-city-files-for-bankruptcy-a-second-time-in-retail-deja-vu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Party City Holdco Inc. 在两年内第二次申请破产，并表示由于销售额在顽固的通货膨胀压力下下滑，将开始关闭其约 700 家门店。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/party-city-files-for-bankruptcy-a-second-time-in-retail-deja-vu</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 06:46:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梅赛德斯明星制造商的倒闭表明汽车业的困境如何打击供应商</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/mercedes-star-maker-s-demise-shows-how-auto-pain-hits-suppliers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国 Gerhardi Kunststofftechnik GmbH 公司经受住了拿破仑入侵、大萧条和两次世界大战的考验。但欧洲目前的汽车业低迷让这家塑料制造商陷入了困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/mercedes-star-maker-s-demise-shows-how-auto-pain-hits-suppliers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
